:NameSpace Utils ‚ćĚ V1.551
‚ćĚ Namespace containing :Includable utility functions
‚ćĚ 2015 11 12 Adam: Auto version + format & layout now handle matrices
‚ćĚ 2016 05 29 DanB: added setupKeys and double quotes for JS
‚ćĚ 2017 05 16 JohnS: Added ]box -t=def functionality
‚ćĚ 2017 05 23 Adam: Added 16.0's new primitives
‚ćĚ 2017 06 12 Adam: Handle when boxing hasn't been initialised
‚ćĚ 2018 02 11 JohnS: Moved functions defs, exports and in to this file.
‚ćĚ 2018 03 13 Adam: repObj recog sysconsts and optional ‚ćļ for parens if needed, ‚ä£, ‚äĘ, Unicode chars
‚ćĚ 2018 03 21 JMS: [15591] improvements to ]defs
‚ćĚ 2018 04 18 Adam: ]??cmd ‚Üí ]cmd -??
‚ćĚ 2018 11 06 Adam: repObj handle complex arithmetic progressions
‚ćĚ 2018 01 17 Adam: [16805] fall back to serialisation if hitting limit
‚ćĚ 2020 05 21 Adam: refactor, [18076] Add Config
‚ćĚ 2020 05 22 Adam: Cleanup
‚ćĚ 2020 05 26 Adam: [18126] display LF as CR
‚ćĚ 2020 05 27 Adam: Add Hoof (‚óč¬®)
‚ćĚ 2020 09 14 Adam: repObj: Full precision DECFs, proper error on ref
‚ćĚ 2020 10 16 Adam: Moved CD from ]CD and added relativeTies
‚ćĚ 2021 01 11 Adam: Prevent layoutPar from hanging
‚ćĚ 2021 01 19 Adam: repObj with guaranteed precision and QA
‚ćĚ 2021 03 24 Adam: Add APLcart API
‚ćĚ 2021 04 01 Adam: Let APLcart cache expire after 1 day
‚ćĚ 2021 04 15 Adam: Handle non-string config values in registry
‚ćĚ 2021 05 09 Adam: Include "]" in bracket axis
‚ćĚ 2021 06 07 Adam: Add ‚éēSE.Dyalog.Utils.ExpandConfig (from ]Get's ExpEnv)
‚ćĚ 2021 07 15 Adam: Use disp and display from dfns.dws but amend for CRLF
‚ćĚ 2021 08 02 Adam: Restore old display that can handle clunky chars
‚ćĚ 2021 08 12 Adam: Add View to view in a read-only Editor window
‚ćĚ 2021 10 20 Adam: ExpandConfig support for ${env:name}
‚ćĚ 2021 11 03 Adam: Handle locked functions
‚ćĚ 2021 11 04 Adam: ExpandConfig support for escapes and choosing syntax
‚ćĚ 2022 07 04 Adam: Make APLcart remove URLs before searching
‚ćĚ 2022 12 07 Adam: ExpandConfig include POSIX extensions (like ~) on POSIX-like OS, and handle errors
‚ćĚ 2023 03 06 Adam: Make APLcart fall back to local table if no internet
‚ćĚ 2023 05 16 Adam: [19376] specify dll if .NET "Core"
‚ćĚ 2023 05 25 Adam: Fix typo in nkds
‚ćĚ 2023 05 30 Adam: Staticise ‚éēUSING as the Core value works in Framework
‚ćĚ 2023 06 30 Adam: Dynamicise ‚éēUSING again as the Core value generates error messages in Framework
‚ćĚ 2024 01 04 Adam: Make CD be non-shy as promised
‚ćĚ 2024 07 29 Adam: [20129] Respect ‚éēPP

