    ‚ąá {old}‚Üźforce CDshy new;OS;is64;t;get;lib;chdir;‚éēML ‚ćĚ Current/Change Directory
    ‚ćĚ empty "new": only report; non-empty "new": change dir
    ‚ćĚ warns about tied files with relative tie names if force=0, skips check if force=1
      ‚éēML‚Üź1
      OS‚Üź3‚ÜĎ‚äÉ# ‚éēWG'APLVersion'
      :If 'Win'‚Č°OS                 ‚ćĚ Under Windows we do the association here because we need
          t‚Üź'A*'[1+80=‚éēDR'']       ‚ćĚ the programs to GET the current directory
          'get'‚éēNA'U Kernel32|GetCurrentDirectory',t,' U >0T' ‚ćĚ Associate Get function
          old‚Üź2‚äÉget 260 260                                   ‚ćĚ in all cases we return the current dir
          'chdir'‚éēNA'U Kernel32|SetCurrentDirectory',t,' <0T' ‚ćĚ Associate Set function
      :Else
          old‚Üź‚äÉ‚éēSH'pwd'
      :EndIf
     
      :If ~0‚ąä‚ćīnew         ‚ćĚ change directory
          :If ~force
              ‚éēSIGNAL(√ó‚ČĘrelativeTies)/‚äā('EN' 24)('Message'('Some files (',('.relativeTies',‚ć®‚ćē‚éēTHIS),') ‚éēNTIEd/‚éēFTIEd with relative names (use left argument 1 to ignore)'))
          :EndIf
     
          :If 'Win'‚Č°OS
             ‚ćĚ chdir returns a single int: 1=ok
              ('Unable to change directory: ',new,': Invalid directory')‚éēSIGNAL(chdir‚äānew)‚Üď22
          :Else
              :Select OS
              :Case 'AIX'
                  is64‚Üź32={z‚Üź‚ćĶ ‚čĄ ‚éēSIZE'z'}‚ć¨
                  lib‚Üź'I libc.a(shr',(is64/'_64'),'.o)|chdir <0T1[]'
              :Case 'Lin'
             ‚ćĚ Extract real name of libc that we are actually using
                  t‚Üź‚äÉ‚éēSH'echo $PPID'
                  t‚Üź‚éēSH'ldd /proc/',t,'/exe'
                  lib‚Üź‚äÉ('^\s*libc\.so\b.*=>\s*(\S*)'‚éēS'\1')t
                  lib‚Üź'I ',lib,'|chdir <0T1[]'
              :Case 'Mac'
                  lib‚Üź'I /usr/lib/libc.dylib|chdir <0T1[]'
                  ‚ćĚ chdir returns a single integer: 0=ok
              :EndSelect
              ‚éēNA lib
              ('Unable to change directory: ',new,': Invalid directory')‚éēSIGNAL(0‚Č†chdir‚äānew)/22
          :EndIf
      :EndIf
