    ‚ąá r‚Üźla txtreplace string;‚éēIO;N;from;to;Fl;Tl;Fp;i;b;ip;n
‚ćĚ Text Pattern Replace
‚ćĚ la is a 2 elements enclosed strings: what to look for, the replacement string.
‚ćĚ Ex: 'abc' 'xxyyzz' will turn all non overlapping 'abc' substrings into 'xxyyzz'
      (Fl Tl)‚Üź‚ćī¬®(from to)‚Üź,¬®la ‚čĄ Fp‚Üź‚ćī‚éēIO‚Üź0 ‚čĄ N‚Üź‚ćīb‚Üźfrom‚ć∑string‚Üź,string
      ‚éēSIGNAL Fl‚Üď11
